739
00:35:57,250 --> 00:35:58,666
She's Cecily's biggest dealer.

740
00:35:58,667 --> 00:35:59,832
Can she get me Sasha's number?

741
00:35:59,833 --> 00:36:01,958
Maybe. Let me call Paula.

742
00:36:03,125 --> 00:36:04,999
